{"dataset":"fineweb2_multilingual/lit_Latn","label":"lit_Latn","row_index":71,"shard":"0000_parquet","bytes":1573,"score_byte_start":0,"score_byte_end":1573,"marin_bpb":1.237,"qwen_bpb":1.2334,"gap_bpb":0.0035,"text":"The show narrates the story of two sisters Preeta and Srishti and their attempt to find their mother Sarla and the dynamics which lead to their acquaintance with the rich and famous \"Luthra\" family. The elder son of Luthra family, Rishabh Luthra, owns a celebrity management firm which manages rock star Abhi Mehra's musical concerts and cricketer Karan Luthra's cricket career. His younger brother Karan Luthra has an effortless swagger and charm that makes him an unabashed Casanova, a playboy because of the star cricketer celebrity status he owns.\nInformacija: Nauja 355 serija (lietuvi\u0161kas prof. \u012fgarsinimas)\n\u017di\u016br\u0117ti serial\u0105 internetu Lemties vingiai 1 Sezonas HD kokybe nemokamai:\nAktoriai:Josifas Baliukevi\u010d, Justinas Barkus, Mindaugas Papinigis, Marius Rep\u0161ys, Mantas Vaitiek\u016bnas\n\u201eRimti reikalai\u201c serialas \u012f vien\u0105 sujungs kriminalin\u0117s dramos ir komedijos \u017eanrus. \u201e Tiek kriminal\u0173, tiek dramos, tiek komedijos matysim po lygiai. Ir meil\u0117s matysim: ir nelaimingos, ir netikros, ir...\nAktoriai:Rebecca Romijn, Christian Kane, Lindy Booth, John Harlan Kim, John Larroquette, Noah Wyle, Matt\nSerialas nukels \u012f magi\u0161k\u0173 paslap\u010di\u0173 ir nuotyki\u0173 pasaul\u012f. Kiekvienas \u0161io serialo \u017ei\u016brovas visi\u0161kai kitaip pasi\u017ei\u016br\u0117s \u012f knyg\u0173 pasaulyje karaliaujan\u010dius bibliotekininkus. Tik retas \u017eino, kad po Niujorko...\nInformacija Mielas lankytojau. J\u016bs \u010dia esate kaip neregistruotas vartotojas. Mes si\u016blome jums u\u017esiregistruoti arba tiesiog prisijungti naudojant savo prisijungimo duomenis, tam, kad gal\u0117tum \u012fkelti bei komentuoti norimas naujienas.","marin_bpb_by_char":[0.0,0.0,0.0,